es as complex systems. Early-warning signals could provide important\ninsights regarding the timing and extent of population response to crises to\ninform policy makers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 23:57:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2020 00:48:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-11"}
