ough deciphering the visual polysemy of verbs, our approach is demonstrated\nto outperform state-of-the-art methods by significant margins on the HICO-DET,\nV-COCO, and HOI-VP databases. Code and data in this paper are available at\nhttps://github.com/MuchHair/PD-Net.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Aug 2020 00:49:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Mar 2021 11:56:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Mar 2021 01:13:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-25"}
