res, which enlightens model\ndesign for further studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Aug 2020 08:55:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Aug 2020 08:09:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-18"}
