y\nlower computational cost. In addition, the LSTC-Tubal will also benefit other\ntasks in modeling large-scale spatiotemporal traffic data, such as\nnetwork-level traffic forecasting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Aug 2020 14:19:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 May 2021 12:58:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 12 Jun 2021 17:19:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-15"}
